      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JAZZY BOO (8) made light work of a wide draw last time with a slick early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing third (17.43) at this track over 300m. Leading chance again. NO IDEA (1) settled down midfield and held his position to the line when finishing 4th (17.48) at this track. Yet to win here but has run some good races. Has a strong record out of this box with six wins and six minor placings from 15 starts. In the mix. CANTARA PEARL (2) had been racing in honest fashion recording three placings in a row before finishing fifth (18.16) at Mt Gambier latest. Has performed well from this box with a win and five minor placings to her name from 10 starts. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. RAVEN ZAYLEE (4) was strongly fancied last time but ran below expectations when fourth (20.36), beaten 6 lengths.",
